asible solution to handle any kind of site such as forums, corporate websites to online stores.<\/p>\n<p>Undoubtedly, WordPress development solutions will help entrepreneurs launch sites quickly. In this blog, we provide quick steps on how to build a WordPress site.<\/p>\n<h2><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter size-full wp-image-8788\" src=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/how-to-build-a-corporate-wordpress-site.jpg\" alt=\"How to Build a Corporate WordPress Site\" width=\"908\" height=\"1200\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/how-to-build-a-corporate-wordpress-site.jpg 908w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/how-to-build-a-corporate-wordpress-site-227x300.jpg 227w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/how-to-build-a-corporate-wordpress-site-775x1024.jpg 775w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/how-to-build-a-corporate-wordpress-site-768x1015.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/wp-content\/uploads\/2021\/02\/how-to-build-a-corporate-wordpress-site-300x396.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 908px) 100vw, 908px\" \/><\/h2>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WordPress_Development_Customization_for_Businesses_and_Startups\"><\/span>WordPress Development &amp; Customization for Businesses and Startups<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>Choose a Theme:<\/strong> It is a critical aspect that forms the basis of WordPress development; however, selecting a WordPress theme is often the most overlooked aspect. A theme is a very important aspect that determines the style and layout of your content. There are hundreds of themes and templates available.<\/p>\n<p>Whether you\u2019re looking for a versatile theme for business with multiple locations spread across geographies, an eCommerce site theme, the theme to showcase your portfolio, or news blogging theme, there\u2019s a theme for every need. There are options to learn about templates to control the layouts of your page or create a custom menu to help users navigate your site.<\/p>\n<p>If you thought it was just about selecting the theme, you are mistaken. Both selecting a theme and customizing a website theme can be a daunting task. You can hire a WordPress developer to customize your fonts, colors, and overall look. One of the biggest benefits of using WordPress is it is easy to change your theme and get a new look across all the pages of your site.<\/p>\n<h2><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"WordPress_Customization_with_Plugins\"><\/span>WordPress Customization with Plugins<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Plugins are the foundation of top-performing WordPress sites and provide the option to add several features to your site such as adding contact forms, improve SEO, increase site speed, create an online store, and much more. You can extend the functionality of the website with plugins available. These plugins allow users to add more engaging elements &amp; functionalities to the website, as well as improve overall website performance right from faster browsing speed to responsive website design. You can add plugins to offer online shopping features, social sharing, forums, and so on.<\/p>\n<p>WordPress developers can create customized plugins that can be modified in the future based on business requirements. You can partner with a WordPress development company specializing in plugin development services based on your needs. <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/hire-wordpress-developers.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WordPress developers<\/a> can create customized plugins that can be modified in the future based on business requirements. You can partner with a WordPress development company specializing in plugin development services based on your needs.<\/p>\n<h4>Finally<\/h4>\n<p>Corporate WordPress Website Development requires a continual effort for optimization based on the latest trends as well as staying abreast of security issues. It is important to partner with a <a href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/wordpress-development.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">WordPress development company<\/a> to maintain design, code as well as fixing bugs or technical glitches.<\/p>\n<p>Perfecting a website entails putting services in place to handle such problems: a content and database backup, a maintenance theme, a good developer and designer, and so on.<\/p>\n<div id=\"ez-toc-container\" class=\"ez-toc-v2_0_47_1 ez-toc-wrap-left counter-hierarchy ez-toc-counter ez-toc-transparent ez-toc-container-direction\">\n<div class=\"ez-toc-title-container\">\n<p class=\"ez-toc-title\">Table of Contents<\/p>\n<span class=\"ez-toc-title-toggle\"><\/span><\/div>\n<nav><ul class='ez-toc-list ez-toc-list-level-1 ' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/essential-elements-of-corporate-wordpress-website-development.html\/#WordPress_Development_Customization_for_Businesses_and_Startups\" title=\"WordPress Development &amp; Customization for Businesses and Startups\">WordPress Development &amp; Customization for Businesses and Startups<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/www.hiddenbrains.com\/blog\/essential-elements-of-corporate-wordpress-website-development.html\/#WordPress_Customization_with_Plugins\" title=\"WordPress Customization with Plugins\">WordPress Customization with Plugins<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Empowering more than 60 million websites which includes nearly 40% of the top 10 million websites, WordPress is one of the most popular content management system solutions. WordPress is widely regarded as the most intuiti